==Taxonomy==
The currently accepted taxonomy is based on the [[List of Prokaryotic names with Standing in Nomenclature]] (LSPN) <ref name="J.P. Euzéby"/> and the [[National Center for Biotechnology Information]].<ref name="Sayers et al."/>

* Genus ''Meiothermus'' <small>Nobre et al. 1996 emend. Albuquerque et al. 2009</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus cateniformans|M. cateniformans]]'' <small>Zhang et al. 2010</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus cerbereus|M. cerbereus]]'' <small>Chung et al. 1997</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus chliarophilus|M. chliarophilus]]'' <small>(Tenreiro et al. 1995) Nobre et al. 1996</small> [''Thermus chliarophilus'' <small>Tenreiro et al. 1995</small>]
** Species ''[[Meiothermus granaticius|M. granaticius]]'' <small>Albuquerque et al. 2010</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus hypogaeus|M. hypogaeus]]'' <small>Mori et al. 2012</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus luteus|M. luteus]]'' <small>Habib et al. 2017</small>
** Species ?''[[Meiothermus rosaceus|M. rosaceus]]'' ♠ <small>Chen et al. 2002</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus roseus|M. roseus]]'' <small>Ming et al. 2016</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus ruber|M. ruber]]'' <small>(Loginova et al. 1984) Nobre et al. 1996</small> [''Thermus ruber'' <small>(ex Loginova et al. 1975) Loginova et al. 1984 nom. rev.</small>]
** Species ''[[Meiothermus rufus|M. rufus]]'' <small>Albuquerque et al. 2010</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus silvanus|M. silvanus]]'' <small>(Tenreiro et al. 1995) Nobre et al. 1996</small> [''Thermus silvanus'' <small>Tenreiro et al. 1995</small>]
** Species ''[[Meiothermus taiwanensis|M. taiwanensis]]'' <small>Chen et al. 2002</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus terra|M. terra]]'' <small>Yu et al. 2014</small>
** Species ''[[Meiothermus timidus|M. timidus]]'' <small>Pires et al. 2005</small>

